    "Eduard Chukhlebov has ties to the powerful founder of Ural Mining Metallurgical Company (UMMC) Iskander Makhmudov.",
    "When Makhmudov reorganized his business, he gave Chukhlebov, one of his managers, a 7.5% stake in UMMC.",
    "Chukhlebov also owns minority stakes in thermal coal producer Kuzbassrazrezugol and transportation company Ugol-Trans through UMMC.",
    "UMMC, which is the biggest zinc, copper and coal producer in Russia, operates more than 300 companies in nine regions of Russia."
